{"type": "article", "id": 19478, "title": "带盆景的鱼缸", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-22T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122351McpKIToQNrWLg3eB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计师 James Beardmore 将水培技术引入到家用物件，设计出带盆景的鱼缸。鱼缸可盛放 20 升的水，上面的盖子有 6 个圆形凹槽，可以种上植物，鱼缸里的水需要替换时就直接浇进了植物里，而植物释放出的氧气也可帮助鱼缸的鱼更好呼吸。让生活在小空间的人们可以接触到更多的自然。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145958zxA0Y8GbEjiKI9u1.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"743\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145959g78jfAiRrlJmheFD.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"574\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.54666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145959S7QTHvtNd8xuMrsF.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"789\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150000vgRpIG7MNAHOjdUJ.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"788\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150000SE6pA5dWbURXw394.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"788\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}